**Segments**

- Based on the type, the global factory automation market can be segmented into Programmable Automation Controller (PAC), Distributed Control System (DCS), Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition (SCADA), Product Lifecycle Management (PLM), Manufacturing Execution System (MES), and others.
- Considering the component, the market can be categorized into Sensors, Industrial Robots, Machine Vision Systems, Control Valves, Human-Machine Interface (HMI), and others.
- In terms of industry vertical, the market segmentation includes Automotive, Chemicals, Food & Beverages, Pharmaceuticals, Oil & Gas, and others.
- Geographically, the market is divided into North America, Europe, Asia-Pacific, South America, and Middle East & Africa.

